---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About | Portfolio" description="About me.">
  <section class="md:mx-28 mx-6 my-0 py-6 pt-[72px] max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] mb-5">About Me</h1>
    <p class="text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] leading-relaxed mb-8">
      Hi I am Chris Um, and I am an undergraduate student from Cornell studying computer science, interested in trading, climate, and technology.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] mb-3">Projects</h2>
    <p class="text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] leading-relaxed mb-3">
      A few projects I am currently focusing on:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-1">
      <li>Personal Website Redesign</li>
      <li>Interactive Portfolio Case Studies</li>
      <li>Design System and Component Library</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] mb-3">Interests</h2>
    <p class="text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] leading-relaxed mb-3">
      Outside of project work, I am especially interested in:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[hsl(var(--foreground))] leading-relaxed space-y-1">
      <li>Learning the markets</li>
      <li>Exploring deep technologies in the climate industry</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
